 as we say, to particular features of what we see.

15:52.020 --> 15:55.020
 The primary example of this, the kind of classic example,

15:55.020 --> 15:57.580
 is if you put a little electrode next to a neuron

15:57.580 --> 15:59.780
 in your visual cortex, or if we put you

15:59.780 --> 16:03.060
