 And it's really an amazing phenomenon,

17:18.140 --> 17:19.740
 it happens very, very fast,

17:19.740 --> 17:21.420
 you never notice that you're doing this,

17:21.420 --> 17:22.340
 but everything is built up

17:22.340 --> 17:26.060
 from these fundamental orientation tuned neurons.

