 And what I eventually would find

18:07.680 --> 18:10.980
 is that that neuron was orientation tuned

18:10.980 --> 18:13.060
 over a particular range of angles,

18:13.060 --> 18:15.240
 it's not only going to respond to vertical lines,

18:15.240 --> 18:16.580
 it's also going to respond to lines

18:16.580 --> 18:19.300
